---
const gaps = [
  {
    title: 'Unclear Messaging',
    body: 'Visitors land on the homepage and can’t tell what you sell, who you’re for, or why you’re different. They bounce.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Weak Calls-to-Action',
    body: '“Contact us” buried in a footer doesn’t close anyone. The page should pull people toward the next step on every screen.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Thin Local SEO',
    body: 'No service pages, no city pages, no FAQs, no real keyword work. Google has nothing to rank, so it doesn’t.',
  },
  {
    title: 'No Real Lead Path',
    body: 'A form floating on a contact page isn’t a lead system. It’s a dead end. Quotes, follow-up, and bookings need a path.',
  },
];
---
<section class="problem" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> The gap</span>
      <h2>It’s not a hustle problem.<br/>It’s a system problem.</h2>
      <p class="lede">
        Most local shops are working hard enough. They’re not lazy. They’re missing structure.
        A great install with a confusing website still loses leads. A good business with a weak online presence still gets passed over.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-grid">
      {gaps.map((g, i) => (
        <article class="card elevate reveal problem-card" style={`transition-delay:${i * 70}ms;`}>
          <div class="row">
            <span class="x" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14"><path d="M6 6 L18 18 M18 6 L6 18" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
            </span>
            <h3>{g.title}</h3>
          </div>
          <p>{g.body}</p>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>

    <p class="closing reveal">
      Most local businesses are better than their website makes them look. That’s the gap we close.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .problem-card .row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .problem-card .x {
    width: 32px; height: 32px;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(255, 95, 95, 0.08);
    color: #FF7A7A;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 95, 95, 0.18);
  }
  .closing {
    margin-top: 48px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    color: var(--white);
    max-width: 720px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
</style>
